22;s:5:"2012 ";i:23;s:5:"2011 ";i:24;s:4:"2011";i:25;s:5:"2011 ";i:26;s:6:"2011  ";i:27;s:4:"2011";i:28;s:4:"2011";i:29;s:4:"2010";i:30;s:4:"2010";i:31;s:4:"2010";i:32;s:5:"2010 ";i:33;s:5:"2010 ";i:34;s:6:"2010  ";i:35;s:5:"2010 ";i:36;s:4:"2009";i:37;s:4:"2009";i:38;s:6:"2008  ";i:39;s:4:"2008";i:40;s:4:"2008";i:41;s:4:"2008";i:42;s:5:"2007 ";i:43;s:5:"2007 ";i:44;s:6:"2007  ";i:45;s:5:"2007 ";i:46;s:4:"2006";i:47;s:4:"2005";i:48;s:5:"2004 ";i:49;s:5:"2004 ";i:50;s:4:"2004";}s:4:"info";a:51:{i:0;s:0:"";i:1;s:0:"";i:2;s:0:"";i:3;s:0:"";i:4;s:0:"";i:5;s:1084:"<strong>On a day-to-day basis</strong>:
I have the wonderful privilege of working to pair Meeting Tomorrow technicians with events nationwide to ensure all events meet the expectations of our clients. 

<strong>The best part of my job is</strong>:
Working with the best team anyone could ask for! The Fulfillment Team works hard to utilize resources nationwide and get the job done, whether the event is on the same day we receive the request, or a year away and we have fun doing it!

<strong>My favorite thing about Meeting Tomorrow is</strong>:
The Culture! Meeting Tomorrow is a community of hard working individuals that enjoy spending time together. We take our jobs very seriously and want nothing more than the satisfaction of the client. The other side of MT culture is how seriously we take our values. Everyone who works here has a dedication to commitment, kindness, and humility in everything we do, within the work we do, as well as in our free time. This is a community that inspires positivity and growth every day and I cannot imagine a better place to work!  ";i:6;s:687:"<strong>On a day-to-day basis</strong>:<br>I make sure our website appears on search engines, such as Google, when people search for AV and technology rental terms. I do this by ensuring that our site is SEO-friendly, publishing useful content, optimizing webpages, and raising awareness of the site.<br /><br /><strong>The best part of my job is</strong>:<br>It's nice to know that if my work brings more search traffic to the site, then we can get more leads and, in turn, more sales!<br /><br /><strong>My favorite thing about Meeting Tomorrow is</strong>:<br>Participating in the community garden, walking around the beautiful neighborhood, and taking a break to pet the office dogs.";i:7;s:554:"<strong>On a day-to-day basis</strong>:<br>Help the sales team prepare production quotes for new customers. Review production sales orders and find the right vendor to fulfill the job. Occasionally travel to event locations and oversee the production.<br /><br /><strong>The best part of my job is</strong>:<br>Getting to see an event go from the planning stage to full execution and thrilling the client by meeting and exceeding expectations.<br /><br /><strong>My favorite thing about Meeting Tomorrow is</strong>:<br>Definitely the people I work with!";i:8;s:807:"<strong>On a day-to-day basis</strong>:<br>As an Account Manager, I assist many different Meeting Tomorrow teams in communicating the appropriate details to ensure a successful client event.  I have the pleasure of building relationships with clients so they are comfortable coming to me to coordinate the details for their events on a specific deadline.<br /><br /><strong>The best part of my job is</strong>:<br>I love coordinating all the little details that go into an order and resolving issues that come up.  I am a detail crazed person so this is my perfect little pocket.<br /><br /><strong>My favorite thing about Meeting Tomorrow is</strong>:<br>The people!  Everyone is so welcoming and friendly which makes for a great working environment.  I feel really lucky to be a part of this growing team.";i:9;s:468:"<strong>On a day-to-day basis</strong>:<br>I work closely with clients on events to provide AV and tech solutions. <br /><br /><strong>The best part of my job is</strong>:<br>Every client and event is different. There's always an opportunity to learn something new. <br /><br /><strong>My favorite thing about Meeting Tomorrow is</strong>:<br>My favorite thing about Meeting Tomorrow is that I'm able to be who I am, and still be apart of something bigger than myself.";i:10;s:0:"";i:11;s:553:"<strong>On a day-to-day basis</strong>:<br>I develop unique event solutions with customers nationwide.<br /><br /><strong>The best part of my job is</strong>:<br>The best part about my job is knowing that no matter what, Meeting Tomorrow values the commitment that we promise to our customers. It is amazing how hard everyone works here to ensure that events run smoothly! <br /><br /><strong>My favorite thing about Meeting Tomorrow is</strong>:<br>My favorite thing about Meeting Tomorrow is the company culture and how well everyone works as a team. ";i:12;s:599:"<strong>On a day-to-day basis</strong>:<br>I'm a part of warehouse operations. I help QC our AV and Tech equipment and help load and unload all the equipment that goes out and comes in. I also help fulfill orders that come through and keep a clean and organized work environment.<br /><br /><strong>The best part of my job is</strong>:<br>The best part of my job is working with outstanding co-workers!<br /><br /><strong>My favorite thing about Meeting Tomorrow is</strong>:<br>The best part of Meeting Tomorrow is our staff. Every department works and treats each other with respect and kindness. ";i:13;s:425:"<strong>On a day-to-day basis I:</strong> <br />Ensure the quality and functionality of the equipment we provide to our customers.<br /><br /><strong>The best part of my job is:</strong> <br />My daily role is never the same from day to day.<br /><br /><strong>My favorite thing about Meeting Tomorrow is:</strong> <br />The encouragement to explore new aspects of the company and the respect everyone has towards each other.";i:14;s:400:"<strong>On a day-to-day basis</strong>:
I work with MT partners to make sure that our clients events go off without a hitch.

<strong>The best part of my job is</strong>:
The best part of my job is having the opportunity to deal with many different people across the country.

<strong>My favorite thing about Meeting Tomorrow is</strong>:
My favorite part about MT is the energetic atmosphere.";i:15;s:260:"<strong>On a day-to-day basis</strong>:
Sell

<strong>The best part of my job is</strong>:
The endless amounts of sales opportunities- overall HUGE potential.

<strong>My favorite thing about Meeting Tomorrow is</strong>: Working with these sweet people.";i:16;s:499:"<strong>On a day-to-day basis</strong>:
I write non-commercial content, update the website, maintain our social media presence, and tackle new marketing projects.

<strong>The best part of my job is</strong>:
I get to be creative and generate real results for our team. I never do the same thing day-to-day!

<strong>My favorite thing about Meeting Tomorrow is</strong>:
The best part of MT is the people I work with. Everyone is sociable, hard-working, team-oriented, and a joy to be around!";i:17;s:294:"<strong>On a day-to-day basis:</strong><br>I find clients the best solutions for their events.<br /><br /><strong>The best part of my job is:</strong><br>Working with clients to build lasting partnerships.<br /><br /><strong>My favorite thing about Meeting Tomorrow is:</strong><br>The people! ";i:18;s:504:"<strong>On a day-to-day basis</strong>:<br>I oversee our Fulfillment teams, manage our overall budgets and make sure we own the best products for our customers' events.<br /><br /><strong>The best part of my job is</strong>:<br>Knowing that my hard work helps everyone around me be more successful.<br /><br /><strong>My favorite thing about Meeting Tomorrow is</strong>:<br>The energy here is amazing. Every team member is constantly working on new ideas to help MT and our customers grow and succeed.  ";i:19;s:519:"<strong>On a day-to-day basis</strong>:<br>My role at MT is to work with my client, providing guidance and solutions, to put on the most successful version of their meeting or event.<br /><br /><strong>The best part of my job is</strong>:<br>I love that I get to work on new challenges every day with the support of an incredible team.<br /><br /><strong>My favorite thing about Meeting Tomorrow is</strong>: My favorite thing about working at Meeting Tomorrow is the friends I've made - both clients &amp; colleagues! ";i:20;s:451:"<strong>On a day-to-day basis</strong>:<br>I am part of the Finance team here at MT. I work on many kinds of reporting and analysis for different departments and also support the Accounting department.<br /><br /><strong>The best part of my job is</strong>:<br>Being surrounded by people who care deeply about their work and this company.<br /><br /><strong>My favorite thing about Meeting Tomorrow is</strong>:<br>Ridiculous jokes that never get old!";i:21;s:247:"<strong>On a day-to-day basis</strong>:<br> I do Accounting & Finance - all sorts of "behind the scenes" fun.<br /><br /><strong>My favorite thing about Meeting Tomorrow is</strong>:<br>The people, the happy energy, the dogs...what's not to like??";i:22;s:501:"<strong>On a day-to-day basis</strong>:<br>My job is to support the Meeting Tomorrow team and help make this a great place to work.<br /><br /><strong>The best part of my job is</strong>:<br>There are so many different aspects of Human Resources - I love that every day is a little bit different.<br /><br /><strong>My favorite thing about Meeting Tomorrow is</strong>:<br>We have a really special company culture that is hard to beat. The people (and the dogs) make me happy to come to work everyday.";i:23;s:868:"<strong>On a day-to-day basis</strong>:<br>All sorts of things! I manage a team of awesome account executives and work on a number of initiatives and projects to help facilitate growth for the team. Every day is different and every day brings a new challenge to overcome which makes it exciting. <br /><br /><strong>The best part of my job is</strong>:<br>That it doesn't feel like a job. Working with all of the really smart, energetic, kind, committed and awesome people makes it exciting to come to work every day.<br /><br /><strong>My favorite thing about Meeting Tomorrow is</strong>:<br>All of the people. Being a part of an organization that truly cares about their employees is so refreshing and I feel lucky every day that I found this company. After the people, it's definitely the bundt cakes that Bryan's mom bakes for us on Thursdays, they're incredible!";i:24;s:367:"<strong>What do you do at Meeting Tomorrow?</strong>:<br>Account Support!!<br /><br /><strong>My favorite thing about Meeting Tomorrow is</strong>:<br>Everybody is genuinely happy to be here everyday, happy and willing to help others and excited about the work we do. Itâs unlike any other environment that Iâve worked in - weâre VERY lucky to be employed here.";i:25;s:0:"";i:26;s:0:"";i:27;s:612:"<strong>On a day-to-day basis</strong>:<br>I create and implement technology solutions for our clients' events. It's important to me that the technology we provide makes our clients' lives easier. I strive for perfectly executed events where the service is second to none.   <br /><br /><strong>The best part of my job is</strong>:<br>Hearing from a client that their event that was successful because of a solution we provided. <br /><br /><strong>My favorite thing about Meeting Tomorrow is</strong>:<br>Working alongside a talented, dynamic group of people that constantly increase my knowledge and skill-set.";i:28;s:528:"<strong>On a day-to-day basis</strong>:<br>I handle logistics planning for all of our mainline orders heading out of our warehouse and help plan the organization and care of our inventory.<br /><br /><strong>The best part of my job is</strong>:<br>The best part of my job is the solid people I have the pleasure of working with on a daily basis.<br /><br /><strong>My favorite thing about Meeting Tomorrow is</strong>:<br>Everyday there is a new problem to solve; I enjoy the constant challenge of an extemporaneous environment.";i:29;s:207:"<strong>What do you do at Meeting Tomorrow?</strong>:<br>I do a lot of random stuff.<br /><br /><strong>My favorite thing about Meeting Tomorrow is</strong>:<br>The dogs, and the people (but the dogs first).";i:30;s:363:"<strong>On a day-to-day basis</strong>:<br>I provide my clients solutions to their AV/Technology event needs while providing the utmost customer service and support.<br /><br /><strong>The best part of my job is</strong>:Creatively solving my client problems<br /><br /><strong>My favorite thing about Meeting Tomorrow is</strong>:<br>The culture and the people! ";i:31;s:453:"<strong>On a day-to-day basis</strong>:<br>I help ensure that our sales team has well-functioning tools and processes that help them provide excellent account management.<br /><br /><strong>The best part of my job is</strong>:<br>Collaborating with people across the entire organization.<br /><br /><strong>My favorite thing about Meeting Tomorrow is</strong>:<br>Enjoying the opportunity to work on one big team of smart and awesome people every day.  ";i:32;s:575:"<strong>On a day-to-day basis</strong>:<br>Work on custom solutions for my clients events. I oversee our medical meetings and virtual meetings and love coming up with the perfect plan for my client events.<br /><br /><strong>The best part of my job is</strong>:<br>Developing strong relationships with my clients to the point where I can talk to them about their personal and professional lives.<br /><br /><strong>My favorite thing about Meeting Tomorrow is</strong>:<br>The flexibility. My work/life balance and supportive colleagues make coming to work really enjoyable.  ";i:33;s:511:"<strong>On a day-to-day basis</strong>:<br>I help clients find solutions to their AV and technology challenges nationwide.<br /><br /><strong>The best part of my job is</strong>:<br>I love learning about all of the amazing events that my clients are putting on across the country!<br /><br /><strong>My favorite thing about Meeting Tomorrow is</strong>:<br>My colleagues feel like family to me and I love coming to work. I know that Meeting Tomorrow cares about me and my personal and professional development! ";i:34;s:329:"<strong>On a day-to-day basis</strong>:<br>I lead the product fulfillment team.<br /><br /><strong>The best part of my job is</strong>:<br>Helping the members of my team develop and grow.<br /><br /><strong>My favorite thing about Meeting Tomorrow is</strong>:<br>It's a comfortable environment that makes me happy to be at work.";i:35;s:345:"<strong>On a day-to-day basis</strong>: I handle all things Human Resources related.<br /><br /><strong>The best part of my job is</strong>:<br>I learn something new every day.<br /><br /><strong>My favorite thing about Meeting Tomorrow is</strong>:<br>The sense of community here and the opportunity to grow, both personally and professionally.";i:36;s:422:"<strong>On a day-to-day basis</strong>:<br>I work on the Client Appreciation Team. I get come up with new, unique ways to make our customers smile!<br /><br /><strong>The best part of my job is</strong>:<br>I get to pick out gifts that make our customers smile!<br /><br /><strong>My favorite thing about Meeting Tomorrow is</strong>:<br>The people! It's great to work in an office where everyone really likes each other! ";i:37;s:269:"<strong>On a day-to-day basis</strong>:<br>I tick and tie with a watchful eye.<br /><br /><strong>The best part of my job is</strong>:<br>The people I sit with, of course!<br /><br /><strong>My favorite thing about Meeting Tomorrow is</strong>:<br>The Emergency Cheeto.";i:38;s:383:"<strong>On a day-to-day basis</strong>:<br>Procure services and gear from a national network of vendors and techs.<br /><br /><strong>The best part of my job is</strong>:<br>Creating relationships with vendors who I can rely on to do a great job for our clients.<br /><br /><strong>My favorite thing about Meeting Tomorrow is</strong>:<br>The great people who make up the work team. ";i:39;s:183:"<strong>On a day-to-day basis</strong>:<br>I fix the broken things.<br /><br /><strong>My favorite thing about Meeting Tomorrow is</strong>:<br>All of you, the dogs and the tech toys.";i:40;s:489:"<strong>My favorite thing about Meeting Tomorrow is</strong>:<br>I wake up every day ready to go to work. Iâve never had that at any other job. Itâs a fun and high paced environment that holds something new and exciting each day of the week. I also enjoy working with other people who are just as passionate about their work as I am. It makes it very easy to work the long hours when necessary because there is a team environment where everyone pushes each other to do their best work.";i:41;s:308:"<strong>On a day-to-day basis</strong>:<br>I manage all our inventory throughout every stage of the rental process.<br /><br /><strong>The best part of my job is</strong>:<br>Equipment repairs.<br /><br /><strong>My favorite thing about Meeting Tomorrow is</strong>:<br>Working with all kinds of crazy gear. ";i:42;s:382:"<strong>On a day-to-day basis</strong>:<br>I manage the teams that make all of our events happen and make sure we execute successfully.<br /><br /><strong>The best part of my job is</strong>:<br>Enabling others to grow and to make an impact on the company.<br /><br /><strong>My favorite thing about Meeting Tomorrow is</strong>:<br>Working with other dedicated and talented people.";i:43;s:533:"<strong>On a day-to-day basis</strong>:<br>Negotiate with partners nationwide to procure equipment and services required to successfully execute challenging / high-level production events.<br /><br /><strong>The best part of my job is</strong>:<br>Being empowered to make any decision I deem necessary to ensure a job's success, and being able to measure that success in a quantifiable manner<br /><br /><strong>My favorite thing about Meeting Tomorrow is</strong>:<br>Being surrounded by such smart, dynamic and fun people all day! ";i:44;s:982:"<strong>On a day-to-day basis</strong>:<br>I help to make the selling lives of the sales team easier. Through fielding sales inquires, either through incoming calls, chats or online requests, I am a liaison between the customer and the sales team. Entering orders for the sales team and collecting accurate documents from customers (to complete their orders) is another important responsibility that I enjoy. I also spend part of each work day following up with every single customer who has recently placed an order with MT. Oh, and if the warehouse needs an address check, they know who to call!<br /><br /><strong>My favorite thing about Meeting Tomorrow is</strong>:<br>One of my favorite things about MT is the camaraderie that we all share. Everyone who works here works and plays very well together. We are continuing to learn as a team and there is no direction for us to go except for up! My most favorite thing about MT is getting greeted by the office dogs every morning!";i:45;s:345:"<strong>On a day-to-day basis</strong>:<br>Administer and customize the software we use to run our company.<br /><br /><strong>The best part of my job is</strong>:<br>Making other people's jobs easier and more efficient through automation.<br /><br /><strong>My favorite thing about Meeting Tomorrow is</strong>:<br>Managing the softball team.  ";i:46;s:705:"<strong>On a day-to-day basis</strong>:<br>I oversee our sales and account teams to ensure we are providing a great experience to our clients.<br /><br /><strong>The best part of my job is</strong>:<br>We are always growing and facing new challenges so every day is different. I love seeing the team develop their skills and grow in their careers. I enjoy seeing a big event come to fruition and celebrating all of our hard work!  <br /><br /><strong>My favorite thing about Meeting Tomorrow is</strong>:<br>I am impressed by the attitude and work ethic of everyone on the team. I appreciate that every employee at MT cares about our clients and is committed to making their events successful at any cost.";i:47;s:358:"<strong>On a day-to-day basis</strong>:<br>I help to ensure our future growth by fostering innovation.<br /><br /><strong>The best part of my job is</strong>:<br>My job is to learn and try new things--what's more exciting than that?<br /><br /><strong>My favorite thing about Meeting Tomorrow is</strong>:<br>I trust, like and admire everyone who works here ";i:48;s:282:"<strong>On a day-to-day basis</strong>:<br>I help coordinate and manage our national events.<br /><br /><strong>The best part of my job is</strong>:<br>Playing with Fudge and Kelsey.<br /><br /><strong>My favorite thing about Meeting Tomorrow is</strong>:My co-workers are awesome. ";i:49;s:538:"<strong>On a day-to-day basis</strong>:<br>My job is to develop and support a world-class team; and to protect and promote our culture of respect and affection.<br /><br /><strong>The best part of my job is</strong>:<br>Seeing what our team can accomplish. Their imagination, problem-solving skills and absolute dedication is inspiring to me.<br /><br /><strong>My favorite thing about Meeting Tomorrow is</strong>:<br>Working with bright, kind and talented people who believe in our mission statement - plus they make me laugh every day!";i:50;s:511:"<strong>On a day-to-day basis</strong>:<br>My title says CEO but my day-to-day role is doing everything I can to support our incredible team do the great work they do, and ensuring we're true to our mission of fostering a culture of respect and affection. <br /><br /><strong>The best part of my job is</strong>:<br>The opportunity to work and build relationships with so many amazing and special people. <br /><br /><strong>My favorite thing about Meeting Tomorrow is</strong>:<br>Without question the people. ";}s:20:"sbg_selected_sidebar";a:1:{i:0;s:18:"a:1:{i:0;s:1:"0";}";}s:32:"sbg_selected_sidebar_replacement";a:1:{i:0;s:17:"a:1:{i:0;s:0:"";}";}s:22:"sbg_selected_sidebar_2";a:1:{i:0;s:18:"a:1:{i:0;s:1:"0";}";}s:34:"sbg_selected_sidebar_2_replacement";a:1:{i:0;s:17:"a:1:{i:0;s:0:"";}";}}}